Wallace C. JONES Junior, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2400 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 28, 2017 SALTER, EMAS and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Following review of appellant's response to this Court's order to show cause, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed as one taken from a non-final, non-appealable order.
